Description: The top class WRC before 17, following 2011-2016 regulation. This is a tribute to this class based on Rally2, using Rally2's body kits, BRC's chassis, and a two layer wing within the projection of the car. Equipped with a special 33mm turbo restrictor, 6-speed sequential paddle shifter and 50/50 clutched transfercase with hydrualic clutch disengage mechanism. Gravel spec has about 300mm of suspension travel and 300mm brake discs.
